Search ZIP codes for a given state

Source: R/zip_lookups.r
search_state.Rd

Search ZIP codes for a given state

search_state(state_abb)

Arguments

state_abb

Two-digit code for a U.S. state

Value

dataframe of all ZIP codes for state defined in state_abb

Examples

search_state('NJ')
